info.title: Sales Scheduling Agreement (A2X)
info.description: The service contains header, item, delivery schedule, and schedule line entities, as well as header and item sub-entities for partners and pricing elements. Once the sales scheduling agreement has been created, the sales scheduling agreement number is sent in the response with the data included in the sales scheduling agreement. If there are any issues when creating, retrieving, updating, or deleting the sales scheduling agreement, the system displays error messages in the response.

x-sap-shortText: Create, read, update, and delete sales scheduling agreements using this synchronous inbound service
